<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #eceae4; padding: 40px 24px; color: #1a1a18; }
  .page { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 48px 52px; box-shadow: 0 6px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.10); }
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .page-header h1 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
  .page-header p { font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 5px; }
  hr.rule { border: none; border-top: 2px solid #f0ede8; margin: 16px 0 24px; }
  .card { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 3px 1fr; border: 1px solid #ebebeb; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; overflow: hidden; }
  .accent { width: 3px; }
  .card-inner { padding: 14px 18px; }
  .card-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr; gap: 16px; align-items: start; }
  .sym-wrap { background: #f8f8f6; border-radius: 7px; padding: 10px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 5px; }
  .sym-label { font-size: 10px; color: #aaa; font-weight: 500; }
  .card-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .keywords { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .kw { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 20px; }
  .desc { font-size: 12px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
  .desc strong { color: #222; font-weight: 600; }
  .example { margin-top: 6px; font-size: 11px; color: #888; font-style: italic; }
  .t1 .accent { background: #378add; } .t1 .kw { background: #e6f1fb; color: #185fa5; }
  .t2 .accent { background: #1d9e75; } .t2 .kw { background: #e1f5ee; color: #0f6e56; }
  .t3 .accent { background: #7f77dd; } .t3 .kw { background: #eeedfe; color: #534ab7; }
  .t4 .accent { background: #ba7517; } .t4 .kw { background: #faeeda; color: #854f0b; }
  .t5 .accent { background: #d85a30; } .t5 .kw { background: #faece7; color: #993c1d; }
  .t6 .accent { background: #639922; } .t6 .kw { background: #eaf3de; color: #3b6d11; }
  .page-footer { margin-top: 28px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #ebebeb; font-size: 11px; color: #ccc; text-align: center; }
  @media print { body { background:#fff; padding:0; } .page { box-shadow:none; border-radius:0; padding:32px 40px; max-width:100%; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Relacionamentos UML</h1>
    <p>Engenharia de Software · Resumo dos 6 tipos de relacionamento</p>
  </div>
  <hr class="rule">

  <!-- 1. Associação -->
  <div class="card t1">
    <div class="accent"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-row">
        <div class="sym-wrap">
          <svg width="130" height="30" viewBox="0 0 130 30">
            <rect x="0" y="5" width="52" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#378add" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="26" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#0c447c" font-weight="600">ClasseA</text>
            <line x1="52" y1="15" x2="98" y2="15" stroke="#378add" stroke-width="1.6" marker-end="url(#m1)"/>
            <rect x="78" y="5" width="52" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#378add" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="104" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#0c447c" font-weight="600">ClasseB</text>
            <defs><marker id="m1" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M2 1L8 5L2 9" fill="none" stroke="#378add" stroke-width="1.5"/></marker></defs>
          </svg>
          <span class="sym-label">linha sólida + seta</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Associação</div>
          <div class="keywords"><span class="kw">estrutural</span><span class="kw">permanente</span><span class="kw">multiplicidade</span></div>
          <div class="desc">Relação duradoura entre classes. Um objeto <strong>conhece e referencia</strong> o outro continuamente. Pode indicar multiplicidade (1, 0..*, 1..*) e navegabilidade.</div>
          <div class="example">Ex: Cliente → Pedido</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. Dependência -->
  <div class="card t2">
    <div class="accent"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-row">
        <div class="sym-wrap">
          <svg width="130" height="30" viewBox="0 0 130 30">
            <rect x="0" y="5" width="52" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#1d9e75" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="26" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#085041" font-weight="600">ClasseA</text>
            <line x1="52" y1="15" x2="98" y2="15" stroke="#1d9e75" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-dasharray="5 3" marker-end="url(#m2)"/>
            <rect x="78" y="5" width="52" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#1d9e75" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="104" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#085041" font-weight="600">ClasseB</text>
            <defs><marker id="m2" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M2 1L8 5L2 9" fill="none" stroke="#1d9e75" stroke-width="1.5"/></marker></defs>
          </svg>
          <span class="sym-label">tracejada + seta</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Dependência</div>
          <div class="keywords"><span class="kw">temporária</span><span class="kw">mais fraca</span><span class="kw">parâmetro/método</span></div>
          <div class="desc">Uma classe <strong>usa outra pontualmente</strong> — como parâmetro ou variável local. Sem vínculo persistente. Mudança em B pode impactar A.</div>
          <div class="example">Ex: Relatório --→ Formatador</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. Realização -->
  <div class="card t3">
    <div class="accent"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-row">
        <div class="sym-wrap">
          <svg width="130" height="30" viewBox="0 0 130 30">
            <rect x="0" y="5" width="46" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#7f77dd" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="23" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#26215c" font-weight="600">Classe</text>
            <line x1="46" y1="15" x2="88" y2="15" stroke="#7f77dd" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-dasharray="5 3"/>
            <polygon points="88,9 100,15 88,21" fill="#fff" stroke="#7f77dd" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <rect x="100" y="5" width="30" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#7f77dd" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="115" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#26215c" font-weight="600">«I»</text>
          </svg>
          <span class="sym-label">tracejada + triângulo vazio</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Realização</div>
          <div class="keywords"><span class="kw">interface</span><span class="kw">contrato</span><span class="kw">implementa</span></div>
          <div class="desc">Classe <strong>cumpre o contrato</strong> de uma interface, implementando todos os seus métodos. Sem herança de código — apenas de assinatura.</div>
          <div class="example">Ex: Gato --▷ IAnimal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. Herança -->
  <div class="card t4">
    <div class="accent"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-row">
        <div class="sym-wrap">
          <svg width="130" height="30" viewBox="0 0 130 30">
            <rect x="0" y="5" width="52" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#ba7517" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="26" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#412402" font-weight="600">Subclasse</text>
            <line x1="52" y1="15" x2="88" y2="15" stroke="#ba7517" stroke-width="1.6"/>
            <polygon points="88,9 100,15 88,21" fill="#fff" stroke="#ba7517" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <rect x="100" y="5" width="30" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#ba7517" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="115" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#412402" font-weight="600">Super</text>
          </svg>
          <span class="sym-label">sólida + triângulo vazio</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Herança (Generalização)</div>
          <div class="keywords"><span class="kw">é-um</span><span class="kw">reutilização</span><span class="kw">especialização</span></div>
          <div class="desc">Subclasse <strong>herda atributos e métodos</strong> da superclasse. Representa relação "é-um". Difere da realização por usar linha <strong>sólida</strong>.</div>
          <div class="example">Ex: Cachorro ——▷ Animal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. Agregação -->
  <div class="card t5">
    <div class="accent"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-row">
        <div class="sym-wrap">
          <svg width="130" height="30" viewBox="0 0 130 30">
            <rect x="0" y="5" width="40" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#d85a30" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="20" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#4a1b0c" font-weight="600">Parte</text>
            <line x1="40" y1="15" x2="78" y2="15" stroke="#d85a30" stroke-width="1.6"/>
            <polygon points="78,9 92,15 78,21 64,15" fill="#fff" stroke="#d85a30" stroke-width="1.3"/>
            <rect x="92" y="5" width="38" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#d85a30" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="111" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#4a1b0c" font-weight="600">Todo</text>
          </svg>
          <span class="sym-label">losango vazio no todo</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Agregação</div>
          <div class="keywords"><span class="kw">todo-parte fraco</span><span class="kw">independente</span></div>
          <div class="desc">Relação todo-parte onde a <strong>parte sobrevive</strong> sem o todo. Ciclos de vida independentes. A parte pode pertencer a mais de um todo.</div>
          <div class="example">Ex: Professor ◇— Departamento</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 6. Composição -->
  <div class="card t6">
    <div class="accent"></div>
    <div class="card-inner">
      <div class="card-row">
        <div class="sym-wrap">
          <svg width="130" height="30" viewBox="0 0 130 30">
            <rect x="0" y="5" width="40" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#639922" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="20" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#173404" font-weight="600">Parte</text>
            <line x1="40" y1="15" x2="78" y2="15" stroke="#639922" stroke-width="1.6"/>
            <polygon points="78,9 92,15 78,21 64,15" fill="#639922" stroke="#639922" stroke-width="1"/>
            <rect x="92" y="5" width="38" height="20" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#639922" stroke-width="1.1"/>
            <text x="111" y="17" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter,sans-serif" fill="#173404" font-weight="600">Todo</text>
          </svg>
          <span class="sym-label">losango cheio no todo</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">Composição</div>
          <div class="keywords"><span class="kw">todo-parte forte</span><span class="kw">dependente</span></div>
          <div class="desc">Relação todo-parte onde a <strong>parte é destruída com o todo</strong>. Ciclo de vida compartilhado. A parte pertence exclusivamente a um único todo.</div>
          <div class="example">Ex: Cômodo ◆— Casa</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="page-footer">Engenharia de Software · Relacionamentos UML · Referência rápida</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
